# Supabase Data Access Guidance

- Centralize Supabase client creation and avoid ad-hoc instantiation in page components.
- Encode tenant scoping in every project/deliverable query path.
- Prefer narrow, explicit selects over broad wildcard fetches.
- Keep write paths idempotent where practical to reduce duplicate handoff events.
- Map database errors to clean domain errors that UI and API layers can handle predictably.
